    public abstract class DefaultResourceHandler<C,E,D,G,L>
extends AbstractResourceHandler<C,E,D,G,L>
    Default implementation of AbstractResourceHandler. If a concrete handler inherits from this class, only the relevant methods should be overridden, and default validator is supplied.
    Author:
    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/
